Package: univention-passwd-store
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends},
 univention-config,
 univention-pam,
 pam-runasroot
Description: UCS - password store
 This package stores the cleartext-passwort while a user is
 logged in. While this decrease system-security it allows
 the user to start applications like rdesktop with a
 "single sign on".
 .
 It is part of Univention Corporate Server (UCS), an
 integrated, directory driven solution for managing
 corporate environments. For more information about UCS,
 refer to: https://www.univention.de/
